Can I advertise with a DBA

Yes, you can advertise with a DBA (Doing Business As) name. However, it's important to ensure that your DBA is properly registered and complies with NewsBreak's advertising policies. For more detailed guidelines, please refer to our Ad Policy document here: [Ad Policy](https://help.newsbreak.com/hc/en-us/articles/25362604231053-Ad-Policy). If you have any specific questions or need further assistance, feel free to reach out!
